\h PILEMO 
\toc1 Ojibiama8agani8i Pilemo 
\toc2 Pilemo 
\mt2 Ojibiama8agani8i 
\mt1 Pilemo 
\imt1 Enadjimomagag oo mazinaigan 
\ip Kitci apitendagoziban aa a8iag Pilemo (Philémon), ki ani teb8etam dac. Mi ini Pon o8idji8aganibanin. 
\ip Teban pejig ka tibenimagani8idj anokitage8inni, Onizim (Onésime) e ijinikazogobanen, Pilemon ka tibenimigopanin. Pilemokag dac ki odji ojimogoban aa Onizim. Kegapitc ogi nagicka8agoban Ponan kibaodimigi8amikag. Ke8in dac Onizim ki ani teb8etam. 
\ip Pon ki inendam kidji koki ki8enija8adjin Oniziman okackaminikag. Pon dac otaji ojibiama8an ini Pilemon. K8ag8edjimagani8i Pilemo kidji koki odapinadjin Oniziman, mina8adj kidji anokitagodjin. K8ag8edjimagani8i kidji ponenimadjin adi ka iji panaagendjin Oniziman, acitc kidji mino toda8adjin tabickotc o8idjiki8en e inenimadjin teb8etamo8inikag. 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Kin Pilemo, ni8idji8aganan ka kitci sagiagidj acitc ni8idji mikimomaganan, kidojibiamon. Nin Pon, kibaodimigi8amig ka teian, egi teb8eta8ag Jesos Christ. Kidjiki8enan Timote (Timothée) ni8idjiig oo kidji ojibiamonan.  
\v 2 Nidojibiama8ananag acitc aa ik8e Appia ka ijinikazodj, ke8in ka teb8etag, acitc aa nabe Anacipas (Archippe) ka ijinikazodj, ka kitci nak8idj kidji 8idjiinak e anokita8aiak Jesos, acitc kakina kodagiag ka teb8etamo8adj ka ma8adjiidi8adj kimigi8amikag. 
\p  
\v 3 Nipagosenimananag Kije Manido Kidadaminan acitc ka Tibeniminak Jesos Christ kidji ca8enimigo8eg acitc kidji minigo8eg pekadendamo8ini. 
\s1 Pilemo osagii8e8in acitc oteb8etamo8in 
\p  
\v 4 Tasin ako aiamieian, kimik8enimin acitc mig8etc nidina Kije Manido kin odji.  
\v 5 Nigi nodan mega adi epitci sagiad8a Kije Manido odanicinabeman acitc adi epitci teb8eta8adj ka Tibendjigedj Jesos.  
\v 6 Nidaiamie eckam eckam kidji mama8ino8ak kina8it ka iji teb8etamak, midac na8adj ke odji ani kikendamakonin kakina mino kegonan ka minigo8ak Jesos Christ.  
\v 7 Nidjiki8e! Kigi kitci min8endamiijinan acitc kigi kitci sogideeckaojinan. Kisagiag mega Kije Manido odanicinabeman acitc kimin8endamiag. 
\s1 Pon ok8ag8edjiman Pilemon  //  kidji mino toda8andjin Oniziman (Onésime) 
\p  
\v 8 E kikeniminan dac epitci sagiad8a kodagiag ka teb8etamo8adj, kikacki 8idamon adi ke inakamigiziaban. E midjinijiak mega Jesos Christikag kidiji tibendagozimin.  
\v 9 Pekic dac kikitci sagiin. Ka8in dac kiga 8idamaosinon adi ke todamaban, na8adj nimin8endan kidji k8ag8edjiminan apitc8in kidji kadjinijaonan. Nin sa dac Pon, ka kitci anicinabe8ian, acitc kibaodimigi8amig ka teian Jesos Christ odji, kipagosenimin oo8e.  
\v 10 Ki8i k8ag8edjimin dac kidji 8idoka8adj aa Onizim, ka tibenimadj kidji anokitaok. Ooma kibaodimigi8amikag nigi 8idjia kidji teb8etag ke8in. Midac maia nig8izis enenimag.  
\v 11 8eckadj ako, ka8in odji pejig ki8idjiigosiban. Nogom dac nikitci 8idjiig, acitc kikitci 8i 8idjiig kekin. 
\p  
\v 12 Nogom dac nikoki pidjinija8a kinikag. Mi maia pejig8an nipimadizi8in ijinijaamaonaban ejinag8ag.  
\v 13 Meg8adj kibaodimigi8amikag e teian min8adjimo8in odji, na8adj nidagi min8endan ki kana8enimagiban ooma kidji gi 8idjiijidj, kidji gi nabickaok adi kegi iji 8idjiijiaban kicpin ki teaban ooma.  
\v 14 Ka8in dac 8in iidi ni8i todasin. Nitam ni8i kikendan adi kin eji nda8endaman, midac iidi ke todaman. Ka8in kikadjinijaosinon kidji mino todaojian. Tiegodj kinada8enimin kinigotc kidji onendaman adi 8a iji 8idjiijian. 
\p  
\v 15 Ne8ad Kije Manido ogi pagidinadog8enan Oniziman 8enibik anodj kidji paba tajikendjin, apanigotc kidji gi 8idjiok apitc koki pi ki8edj kimigi8amikag.  
\v 16 Aja nogom ka8in kidanokitage8innim ka motci tibenimadj apitendagozisi, na8adj kiabadj a8acamej apitendagozi apitc8in ka tibenimagani8idj anokitage8inni. Kidjiki8e ka kitci sagiadj apitendagozi, e teb8etag ke8in. Nin, nikitci sagia. Kin dac na8adj kiabadj kida sagia, kidanokitag mega acitc kidjiki8e apitendagozi, e midjinijieg e teb8eta8eg ka Tibendjigedj. 
\p  
\v 17 Kicpin dac ni8idji8agan inenimijian, kiga pidigea kimigi8amikag, tabickotc nin ke todaojiaban.  
\v 18 Kicpin ki madji todaok, kek8an ki kimodimik kegoni, kiga 8idamaojinan, nin dac kiga kijikaon.  
\v 19 Nin tibina8e kidojibiamon oo8e. Nin Pon teb8e kiga koki ki8e kijikaon. Anic dac ka8in 8anikeken adi kagi apitci mino todaonan, egi 8idjiinan kekin kidji ani teb8eta8adj Jesos.  
\v 20 Nidjiki8e! Kipagosenimin iidi kidji iji todaman ka iji k8ag8edjiminan, e sagiadj ka Tibendjigedj. Jesos Christikag kidiji mama8isemin, sogideeckaocin dac. 
\p  
\v 21 Oo ka taji ojibiigeian, kiketcinamenimin kidji todaman adi eji k8ag8edjiminan. Kikikenimin 8a8adj a8acamej kiabadj kidji ijitcigean.  
\v 22 Kodag kegon ki8i k8ag8edjimin acitc. Ojitamaocin kenin adi ke iji tajikeian kimigi8amikag. Niketcinamendan mega Kije Manido kidji ndotago8eg adi ka iji k8ag8edjimeg, midac kidji gi koki pi nda 8abaminagok. 
\s1 Ick8eag anamikodadi8inan 
\p  
\v 23 Epapanas (Épaphras) ke8in te ooma kibaodimigi8amig osa mega oteb8eta8an Jesos Christan. Kidanamikag dac.  
\v 24 Mak (Marc) acitc Anistakos (Aristarque) acitc Demas acitc Lok (Luc) ka 8idji mikimomag8a, kidanamikagog ke8ina8a. 
\p  
\v 25 8egona ca8enimigo8eg ka Tibendjigedj Jesos Christ kina8a kakina. 
\cls Nin Pon